# STEP 2Ô∏è‚É£ ‚Äì CHECK: Are Pages Visible?

### API Call

GET https://graph.facebook.com/v19.0/me/accounts

Authorization: Bearer AXGEN\_SYSTEM\_TOKEN

  

### Example Response

{

¬†¬†"data": \[

¬†¬†¬†¬†{

¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†"id": "1234567890",

¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†"name": "Client Brand Page",

¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†"access\_token": "PAGE\_TOKEN",

¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†"tasks": \["ADVERTISE", "ANALYZE", "CREATE\_CONTENT"\]

¬†¬†¬†¬†}

¬†¬†\]

}

  

### Interpretation

| Condition | Meaning |
| --- | --- |
| data empty | ‚ùå Page not assigned |
| page present | ‚úÖ Page access OK |
| missing ADVERTISE | ‚ö†Ô∏è Ads permission missing |
